title: 8 May 1945 Stadium
text: The 8 May 1945 Stadium (, ) is a multi-use <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="S%C3%A9tif">Sétif</a>, Algeria. It is currently used mostly for <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> matches and is the home ground of <a href="ES%20S%C3%A9tif">ES Sétif</a>. The stadium holds 25,000 people.
